title: Hooker's six TDs rally Park Center to 48-37 victory over Cooper
text: Hooker's six TDs rallies Park Center to 48-37 victory at Cooper 10/20/2015, 10:00pm CDT By David La Vaque, Star Tribune The senior caught three scoring passes, ran for two scores and returned an interception for a touchdown. Amani Hooker of Park Center returned an interception for a touchdown in the fourth quarter of the game with Cooper on Tuesday. Hooker scored six touchdowns.
